    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Java中使用akka手记二 Cluster]]></title>
    <link href="http://2014.54chen.com/blog/2014/04/16/how-to-use-akka-in-java-2/"/>
    <updated>2014-04-16T15:12:32+08:00</updated>
